title: UFYB 8: How to Stop Settling
itunes:title: How to Stop Settling
description:
Today, I want to talk to you about settling – what it’s all about, why you do it, and the harmful effects of settling. Listen in to discover why you should consider putting an end to your stagnation and scarcity thinking and how you can stop settling and start living a full, extraordinary life.

Get full show notes and more information here: http://bit.ly/2BkIBg6
